                "Session ID length must be positive. Provided: " + length
            );
        }

        // Calculate the number of bytes needed to produce the desired length
        // after Base64 encoding (each 3 bytes become 4 Base64 characters)
        int byteLength = (int) Math.ceil(length * 3.0 / 4.0);

        // Generate random bytes
        byte[] randomBytes = new byte[byteLength];
        SECURE_RANDOM.nextBytes(randomBytes);

        // Encode to Base64 and remove padding characters
        String base64String = Base64.getEncoder().withoutPadding()
            .encodeToString(randomBytes);

        // Trim or extend to exact length (very rare case where length doesn't match)
        if (base64String.length() > length) {
            return base64String.substring(0, length);
        } else if (base64String.length() < length) {
            // Append random characters if shorter than desired (shouldn't happen with proper calculation)
            return base64String + generate(length - base64String.length());
        }

        return base64String;
    }
}
